data.description: Absolute beautiful home with gorgeous views in the Victory area of Portsmouth. This home comes with 3 bedrooms, 2 full bathrooms, and a downstairs half bathroom. It is very spacious with more than 1900 sq feet of living space. There is also an office space that could be used as an extra bedroom if you desire. Brand new carpet throughout the home. The home also comes with solar panels!     Amenities include lawn care, cable package, pool, and clubhouse!     You are going to want to see this one!    Offering 3% CLOSING COST ASSISTANCE!
